                        <a href="http://openstack.org/software/start/" class="overview-btn right-btn">Get The Software <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-down"></i></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="release-text">Latest Release: Icehouse (May 2014)</div>
                </div>
